        <p class="lede-p">Local listing management is the unglamorous plumbing of local SEO. <strong>One inconsistent suite number across 40 directories</strong> can quietly drag a 4-location dental group out of the local pack. The right tool keeps NAP consistent, suppresses duplicates, and pushes updates across the network without you babysitting forty separate logins.</p>

        <p>We ran 10 listing platforms across 17 real locations for 90 days — a single-location law firm, a 4-location dental group, and a 12-location home services brand. Here is the ranking by what each tool actually delivers on coverage, accuracy, and per-location cost.</p>

