        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Don't want to run another listing dashboard?</h4>
            <p>theStacc handles listings, local pages, GBP posts, and citation cleanup as one managed service. <strong>$49/mo Local SEO, $167/mo full bundle</strong> — one bill, no per-location math.</p>
